channel.title: APBS
channel.description:
Files from APBS APBS is a software package for the numerical solution of the Poisson-Boltzmann equation, a popular continuum model for describing electrostatic interactions between molecular solutes over a wide range of length scales. <http://www.poissonboltzmann.org/>.
Please register at http://goo.gl/LGVU5j before downloading!
